Gävle.title: Gävle
Gävle.byline: Gävle is a port on the Baltic Sea in Gävleborg County, the southernmost part of Norrland.

Gävleborg County.title: Gävleborg County
Gävleborg County.byline: Gävleborg County, Gävleborgs län, consists of two provinces, Gästrikland and Hälsingland, which make up the southernmost part of Norrland in Sweden.
